---
title: Bacon and Cheese Stuffed Burgers with Crisp Salad and Ranch Dressing
description: It's a bacon-stuffed burger extravaganza! Crumbled bacon is mixed with cream cheese and hidden inside juicy beef burgers. These beauties are finished off with pickles and tomatoes, then served with a zesty ranch salad, for the very best burger dinner!
